text: Carina Gustavsson (born 24 March 1962) is a Swedish rower. She competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Ängelholm Municipality
